OL,3,C'A death sentence': Millions of Afghan
OL,4,Crefugees face deportation from Pakistan
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Michael
OL,7,FMaitland-Jones, with translation by
OL,8,FMohammad Noman
OL,10,FFor Shakoofa, Pakistan has been home
OL,11,Ffor nearly three years.
OL,13,FOnce a humanitarian worker for a US-
OL,14,Ffunded programme in Afghanistan, she,
OL,15,Falong with thousands of others, found
OL,16,Fherself vulnerable to persecution
OL,17,Ffollowing the Taliban's return to
OL,18,Fpower in 2021.
