OL,3,C'A death sentence': Millions of Afghan
OL,4,Crefugees face deportation from Pakistan
OL,6,FNeighbouring Pakistan, historically a
OL,7,Fplace of refuge for some Afghans, was
OL,8,Fwhere she went in 2022.
OL,10,F"To save my life, as well as that of
OL,11,Fmy husband and daughter, I left
OL,12,FAfghanistan," Shakoofa said.
OL,14,FWe are only using her first name in
OL,15,Forder to protect her identity.
