OL,3,C'A death sentence': Millions of Afghan
OL,4,Crefugees face deportation from Pakistan
OL,6,FNow though, she ` along with up to
OL,7,Fthree million other Afghans ` faces
OL,8,Fbeing forcibly returned to her home
OL,9,Fcountry as the Pakistani government
OL,10,Framps up an ambitious plan of mass-
OL,11,Fdeportations for those they say are
OL,12,Fthere illegally.
