OL,3,C'A death sentence': Millions of Afghan
OL,4,Crefugees face deportation from Pakistan
OL,6,FIn January, US President Donald Trump
OL,7,Fissued an executive order suspending
OL,8,Fthe US refugee programme, leaving
OL,9,FAfghans like Shakoofa, who were
OL,10,Frelying on it, helpless.
OL,12,F"The days are full of stress and
OL,13,Fanxiety ` on the one hand the
OL,14,Funcertainty and on the other the fear
OL,15,Fof being arrested," she said.
OL,17,FIt is still better than what she
OL,18,Fbelieves waits for her back home under
OL,19,Fthe de facto Taliban government.
