OL,3,C'A death sentence': Millions of Afghan
OL,4,Crefugees face deportation from Pakistan
OL,6,F"I will lose my life or I will be
OL,7,Farrested and tortured, returning or
OL,8,Fbeing deported to Afghanistan would be
OL,9,Fa death sentence for me," she said.
OL,11,FAs the official deadline for Afghan
OL,12,Fmigrants to leave voluntarily expired
OL,13,Fthis week, police have been increasing
OL,14,Ftheir presence and Shakoofa said she
OL,15,Fhas been unable to leave her house as
OL,16,Fshe lacks the correct visa.
