OL,3,C'A death sentence': Millions of Afghan
OL,4,Crefugees face deportation from Pakistan
OL,6,FIt's not the first time that Afghans
OL,7,Fin Pakistan have faced uncertainty
OL,8,Fabout the future ` since the first
OL,9,Fwave of deportations began in 2023
OL,10,Fover 800,000 have been expelled.
OL,12,FCaught up in this are some who have
OL,13,Fcalled Pakistan their home their
OL,14,Fentire lives.
OL,16,FAhmad Shahab was born in a refugee
OL,17,Fcamp in Peshawar in the north-west of
OL,18,Fthe country. He is 30 now.
