OL,3,C'A death sentence': Millions of Afghan
OL,4,Crefugees face deportation from Pakistan
OL,6,F"We came to Pakistan because the
OL,7,FRussians invaded Afghanistan, and
OL,8,Flater there was a civil war in our
OL,9,Fcountry. Because of these reasons, our
OL,10,Fparents migrated here," he told ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,FIn the past week he, like Shakoofa,
OL,14,Fhas noticed a change in the behaviour
OL,15,Fof authorities.
