OL,6,F"Arrests of refugees have increased a
OL,7,Flot, and the treatment we face is
OL,8,Fworsening," he said. "We are living in
OL,9,Ffear. If we go out looking for work,
OL,10,Fwe do it very cautiously and quickly,
OL,11,Fand we mostly stay hidden in our
OL,12,Fhomes."
OL,14,FTrust in their neighbours has also
OL,15,Fgone.
OL,17,F"We are scared someone might inform on
OL,18,Four house. We have seen many fellow
OL,19,Frefugees who had to leave their
OL,20,Fbelongings behind and were forcefully
OL,21,Fdeported under terrible conditions."
