OL,6,FWork is a concern for him ` he runs a
OL,7,Fsmall business but has no idea how he
OL,8,Fwill start afresh if he has to return
OL,9,Fto Afghanistan. He also has two
OL,10,Fsisters studying in Peshewar who would
OL,11,Flose their right to education if they
OL,12,Fwere back living under the Taliban.
OL,14,FThe deportations have already drawn
OL,15,Fcondemnation from aid agencies and the
OL,16,FUN.
