OL,6,FZaman Sultani, a researcher at Amnesty
OL,7,FInternational, said that while much of
OL,8,FPakistan's deportation plan is still
OL,9,F"shrouded in secrecy", the
OL,10,Fconsequences of it could be disastrous
OL,11,Ffor a country already on the brink.
OL,13,F"Afghanistan is now the second-largest
OL,14,Fhumanitarian crisis worldwide," he
OL,15,Ftold ITV News.
