OL,6,F"You have more than half of the
OL,7,Fpopulation who are dependent on
OL,8,Fhumanitarian assistance to do their
OL,9,Fday-to-day living ... There will be
OL,10,Fadditional pressure on the
OL,11,Fhumanitarian need in the country that
OL,12,Fis mainly handled and delivered by the
OL,13,FUN," he said.
OL,15,FHe added that the Taliban's policy of
OL,16,Fviolent persecution continues against
