OL,9,FTaliban," he said.
OL,11,FThe deportations in Pakistan are
OL,12,Fhappening against a backdrop of other
OL,13,Fworld leaders threatening to carry out
OL,14,Fsimilar programmes, most notably
OL,15,FDonald Trump.
